->  Users Journey Map:

1. /start
    - send message
2. /find
    - send message
3. chat was not found
    - waiting for a chat
4. chat was found
    - chat was stopped unexpectedly
5. send voice
    - send text message or other types of messages
6. get voice

7. /stop
    - waiting for new chat

